Description: Game by JCO, released in 2015
 Safety First!
 An innovative physics puzzler with focus on sound and game design.
 First presented at Revision 2015, Game Competition
 .
 About the game:
 Safety First! is a physics puzzler in which you have to fix broken electric
 wires using your magical yellow repair liquid (myrl).

